T02D2759:137b-0: @137b * // 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs po ta la ke ri'i rtse mo pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2759:137b-2: ri mchog dkyel 'khor rgyal po khyod //
T02D2759:137b-3: ces 'byung ba'i sgrub pa'i thabs bshad par bya'o //
T02D2759:137b-4: thugs rje yi stobs ri mchog rtser //
T02D2759:137b-5: nyi shu rtsa lnga'i bdag nyid ston //
T02D2759:137b-6: 'jig rten gsum mgon la btud de //
T02D2759:137b-7: de yi sgrub thabs mdor bsdus bri //
T02D2759:137b-8: dang por re zhig rnal 'byor gyi dbang phyug tshangs
T02D2759:137b-9: pa'i gnas bzhis yid nye bar brlan par byas la
T02D2759:137b-10: / bsam gtan gyi khang bu la sogs pa'i gnas
T02D2759:137b-11: mal gang yin pa po ta la keri'i rgyal por
T02D2759:137b-13: der gzhal med khang rin chen sna bdun gyi rang bzhin bkod pa phun sum tshogs par bkod pa //
T02D2759:138a-0: 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug 'khor gyi dkyil 'khor dang bcas pa mngon par @138a * //
T02D2759:138a-3: hr'i:/ 'dam skyes sdong bu 'dab brgyad dbus //
T02D2759:138a-4: bdag nyid 'jig rten dbang phyug bskyed //
T02D2759:138a-5: de ni zla mdog skyil krung phyed //
T02D2759:138a-8: shar sogs phyogs dang mtshams rim bzhin //
T02D2759:138a-10: phyogs kyi kha dog gzhon nu'i tshul //
T02D2759:138a-11: gter chen bum pa bzhis gang ba'o //
T02D2759:138a-13: de mthar 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad la //
T02D2759:138a-14: phyogs mi phyogs kyi kha dog can //
T02D2759:138a-15: gti mug rdo rje sgrol ma can //
T02D2759:138a-16: bag chags rdo rje rdo rje 'dzin //
T02D2759:138a-17: 'dod chags rdo rje zhags pa thogs //
T02D2759:138a-18: zhe sdang rdo rje ral gri bsnams //
T02D2759:138a-20: byang shar la sogs mtshams bzhi yum //
T02D2759:138a-21: brtan pa'i rdo rje ri rab 'dzin //
T02D2759:138a-22: sbyor ba'i rdo rje zla ba dang //
T02D2759:138a-23: 'bar ba'i rdo rje nyi ma can //
T02D2759:138a-24: stobs kyi rdo rje ba dan thogs //
T02D2759:138a-25: kha dog phyed gzugs sgeg mo'i tshul //
T02D2759:138a-27: khyams kyi shar sogs phyogs bzhir yang //
T02D2759:138a-28: phyogs mdog gar gyis rol pa mo //
T02D2759:138a-29: rdo rje gzugs mdzes me long can //
T02D2759:138a-30: rdo rje sgra snyan pi wang bsgreng //
T02D2759:138a-31: rdo rje dri mchog byung pa thogs //
T02D2759:138a-32: rdo rje ro bzangs zhal zas 'dzin //
T02D2759:138a-34: de bzhin byang shar sogs grva bzhir //
T02D2759:138a-35: rdo rje reg ma gos mchog thogs//
T02D2759:138a-36: rdo rje chos ma chos 'byung can //
T02D2759:138a-38: rdo rje snang ma sgron ma thogs //
T02D2759:138a-39: yid 'ong phyogs phyed mdog can la'o //
T02D2759:138a-41: de nas shar sogs sgo bzhir yang //
T02D2759:138a-42: lcags kyu zhags pa lcags sgrog dril //
T02D2759:138a-43: phyogs mdog cung zad khro ba'i tshul //
T02D2759:138a-44: de ltar kun phyag g-yon padmo //
T02D2759:138a-45: brtson pa'i cha byad pad zla la //
T02D2759:138a-46: rang gi sa bon las gyur mtshungs //
T02D2759:138a-47: de rjes sgyu ma ting 'dzin la //
T02D2759:138a-48: gnas nas dag pa rtogs par bya //
T02D2759:138a-49: gnas dang lus rab rnam par dag / dkyil 'khor 'khor lo zhes byar brjod //
T02D2759:138a-50: de bzhin lus dang sems rab dag / nyi shu lnga yi bdag nyid do //
T02D2759:138a-52: de nas ye shes dkyil 'khor lha //
T02D2759:138a-53: ji bzhin bkug la mchod sogs bcas //
T02D2759:138a-54: gsol btab dam tshig mthu bskyed de //
T02D2759:138a-55: rig pa'i ting 'dzin ldan pas bzlas //
T02D2759:138a-56: aom a'a:hr'i:po ta la ke ru tu ma h'a k'a ru n'i ka h'um h'um phat sv'a h'a /
T02D2759:138b-1: ao aoo aam aa:ka tsa ta ta /
T02D2759:138b-5: gal te dmigs pa'i sbyor ba yis //
T02D2759:138b-6: skyo bar gyur na sbyor bral ba //
T02D2759:138b-7: shin tu dmigs med zhi ba'i rgyu //
T02D2759:138b-8: mkhas pas rdzogs pa'i rim pa bsgom //
T02D2759:138b-9: nam zhig de las ldang 'dod tshe /
T02D2759:138b-10: snying rje chen pos blo bskyed la //
T02D2759:138b-11: dpal ldan nyi shu rtsa lnga'i bdag / dkyil 'khor mchod sogs bya phyir 'bad //
T02D2759:138b-12: bdun phrag gcig gam gnyis sam gsum //
T02D2759:138b-13: ji ste brgya'am bdun phrag bcus //
T02D2759:138b-14: dam tshig bsam gtan ldan spyod la //
T02D2759:138b-15: dngos grub the tshom mi bya'o //
T02D2759:138b-16: rdo rje 'dzin pas rgyud dang ni //
T02D2759:138b-17: bla ma sangs rgyas 'drar bshad de //
T02D2759:138b-18: rgyud bral bla ma spangs pa la //
T02D2759:138b-19: dngos grub yod par ma gsungs phyir //
T02D2759:138b-20: mtshan ma tsam mthong bdag gis 'dir //
T02D2759:138b-21: bla ma'i gsung gi rgyud don bsdus //
T02D2759:138b-23: ri mchog nam zhig bgrod par 'gyur //
